<span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Alon_Ben-Meir&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Journalism and media"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span>
</div>
